These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, colombian, french, british, turkish, polish, australian
1. the turkish is between the french and the colombian##2
2. the polish is on the right of the thai##1
3. the australian is on the right of the british##1
4. the polish is in the middle##1
5. the colombian is in an odd position##4
6. the french is on the left of the turkish##1
7. the thai is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | british | australian | thai | polish | french | turkish | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, rugby, lacrosse, cricket, skiing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Sport   | cricket | cycling | skiing | surfing | lacrosse | rugby | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, manager, fisherman, lawyer, chef
1. the social-worker is on the right of the chef##1
2. the bartender is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the doctor is on the left or right of the manager##3
4. the fisherman is on the left or right of the chef##3
5. the manager is on the left of the bartender##1
6. the bartender is on the left of the fisherman##1
7. the social-worker is in an even position##4
8. the bartender is on the left of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Job   | doctor | manager | bartender | fisherman | chef | social-worker | lawyer |

