.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, skateboarding, climbing, handball, volleyball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | cricket | sailing | climbing | volleyball | handball | skateboarding | rugby |

