.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, sprite, fanta, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
6. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Beverage   | milk | fanta | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | sprite | cola |

