5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
