.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-9::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, cat, goat, rat, dog, ferret
1. the owner of the goat is the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |     3      |   4    |   5    |  6   |   7   |
| Pet   | cat | ferret | bird | rat | dog | guinea-pig | goat |

