1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
4. the fan of metal is in the middle##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
6. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |  3   |  4   |  5   |     6     |  7  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | reggae | metal | salsa | trance | disco |

