.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-13::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter, boat, bike, motorbike, roller, helicopter
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
8. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6  |  7  |
| Transport   | scooter | bike | motorbike | boat | roller | helicopter | snowmobile |

