.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, skateboard, trike, car, bus, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 8. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Transport   | scooter | motorbike | jet-ski | trike | car | skateboard | bus |

 